linguacast/
│
├── app/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── main.py                    # FastAPI entrypoint
│
│   ├── api/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   └── routes.py              # API routes (upload, status check)
│
│   ├── chunker/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   └── chunker.py             # Audio chunking using FFmpeg
│
│   ├── transcriber/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   └── transcribe_chunks.py   # Whisper-based transcriber
│
│   ├── workers/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   └── background_worker.py   # Thread pool, job queue, job manager
│
├── uploads/                       # Uploaded audio files
├── chunks/                        # Temporary chunks (auto-deleted after use)
├── transcripts/                   # (Optional) Store final transcripts if needed
├── requirements.txt               # Python dependencies
├── README.md                      # Project overview
├── .gitignore                     # Git ignore config
└── test_chunk.py                  # Test script (optional)
